speech:
"First! Let people know about quitting smoking."

Second! Create a new atmosphere and enjoy hobbies

Third! Rest in peace during withdrawal symptoms

Fourth! Throw away the lighter, ashtray, etc

Fifth! Brushing your teeth right after you eat

Sixth! Drink water when you want to smoke!

Seventh! Stay away from smoking places and people!

Eighth! Don't hold a cigarette in your mouth!

9th! Eating foods that are high in fiber

Number 10! Avoid coffee and soda!

★ Remember when you quit smoking The Ten Commandments for No Smoking ★"
